pan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E20%3C%2Fspan%3EAfter%20the%20flood%2C%20Noah%20began%20to%20cultivate%20the%20ground%2C%20and%20he%20planted%20a%20vineyard.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22gene_9_21%22%20bk%3D%22gene%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2221%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E21%3C%2Fspan%3EOne%20day%20he%20drank%20some%20wine%20he%20had%20made%2C%20and%20he%20became%20drunk%20and%20lay%20naked%20inside%20his%20tent.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22gene_9_22%22%20bk%3D%22gene%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E22%3C%2Fspan%3EHam%2C%20the%20father%20of%20Canaan%2C%20saw%20that%20his%20father%20was%20naked%20and%20went%20outside%20and%20told%20his%20brothers.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22gene_9_23%22%20bk%3D%22gene%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E23%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Shem%20and%20Japheth%20took%20a%20robe%2C%20held%20it%20over%20their%20shoulders%2C%20and%20backed%20into%20the%20tent%20to%20cover%20their%20father.%20As%20they%20did%20this%2C%20they%20looked%20the%20other%20way%20so%20they%20would%20not%20see%20him%20naked.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22gene_9_24%22%20bk%3D%22gene%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2224%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E24%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20Noah%20woke%20up%20from%20his%20stupor%2C%20he%20learned%20what%20Ham%2C%20his%20youngest%20son%2C%20had%20done.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22gene_9_25%22%20bk%3D%22gene%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E25%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20he%20cursed%20Canaan%2C%20the%20son%20of%20Ham%3A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-sp%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BMay%20Canaan%20be%20cursed!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EMay%20he%20be%20the%20lowest%20of%20servants%20to%20his%20relatives.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22